OL,4,G0140FDown The Tracks: The Music That
OL,5,     FInfluenced Bob Dylan
OL,6,     GBob Dylan has influenced an
OL,7,     Gentire generation of musicians.
OL,8,     GBut who influenced him? This
OL,9,     Gdocumentary explores the work of
OL,10,     Gthose who shaped his music.
OL,11,G0340FBob Dylan: The Other Side Of the
OL,12,     FMirror
OL,13,     GVenture back to the 60s in this
OL,14,     Gfilm from Murray Lerner,
OL,15,     Gfeaturing Bob Dylan's appearances
OL,16,     Gat the Newport Folk Festival and
OL,17,     Gexploring his rise to musical
OL,18,     Gstardom.
