OL,4,G0510FDiscovering: Crosby, Stills, Nash
OL,5,     F& Young
OL,6,     GA look at the late David Crosby's
OL,7,     Gfolk-rock super group - Crosby,
OL,8,     GStills, Nash & Young - famed for
OL,9,     Gtheir vocal harmonies and fiery
OL,10,     Ginterpersonal relationships.
OL,11,G0535FDiscovering: Neil Young
OL,12,     GFrom Crazy Horse to Crosby,
OL,13,     GStills, Nash & Young, Neil Young
OL,14,     Gwas a driving force behind some
OL,15,     Gof the biggest groups of the 60s
OL,16,     Gbefore finding huge success on
OL,17,     Ghis own.
